    IInfoflowSolver

    public class InfoflowSolver
extends heros.solver.PathTrackingIFDSSolver<soot.Unit,Abstraction,soot.SootMethod,soot.jimple.toolkits.ide.icfg.BiDiInterproceduralCFG<soot.Unit,soot.SootMethod>>
implements IInfoflowSolver
    We are subclassing the JimpleIFDSSolver because we need the same executor for both the forward and the backward analysis Also we need to be able to insert edges containing new taint information
